that Aerotaur fired hit him in the right shoulder.  3 of the shots Aquataur 
fired and 1 of the shots Terrataur fired hit Apewing in the right 
shoulderblade.  Apewing's right wing failed him for a second and Apewing 
falls to the ground.  But, just before he crashed to the ground, his right 
wing started working again and he flew back up in the air

   "Is that all you got, you piece of Slag?"  Apewing yells at Aerotaur.

   Apewing takes his missle launcher and fires two missles at Aerotaur, he 
then flies up in the air to make distance between him and his attackers.
